vulnerabilities.title: email-existence Inefficient Regular Expression Complexity vulnerability
vulnerabilities.description: A vulnerability was found in email-existence. It has been rated as problematic. Affected by this issue is some unknown functionality of the file `index.js`. The manipulation leads to inefficient regular expression complexity. The name of the patch is 0029ba71b6ad0d8ec0baa2ecc6256d038bdd9b56. It is recommended to apply a patch to fix this issue. VDB-216854 is the identifier assigned to this vulnerability.
